title: Stock market news live updates: Stocks dip after S&P 500 closes at highest level since Jan. - Yahoo Finance
content: Stock market news live updates: Stocks dip after S&P 500 closes at highest level since Jan.  Yahoo Finance
description: U.S. stocks drifted slightly lower after rallying earlier this week, as investors eyed developments on discussions between Russia and Ukraine and mulled mixed data on the U.S. economy.
